Shoreward Revenant banishment
-1 3 1 1 70 80 5806 7000 6 3500000 0
5819
The Shoreward Revenant, a dead Assessor who administered the jurisdictional boundary at the Shoreward Threshold during the Iseth Reach's final season, has refused to acknowledge the end of its commission. It now enforces obsolete crossing protocols with lethal certainty, blocking legitimate transit and killing any traveler who fails its archaic certification review. The Tidemouth Warden post commander has exhausted conventional responses and requires the Revenant's permanent banishment.
The Shoreward Revenant has been banished and the Shoreward Threshold is open to legitimate transit. Tidemouth Warden patrols have conducted a full crossing of the jurisdictional boundary for the first time in recent memory without fatality. The post commander has notified the Mafdet Harbor Authority that the eastern Reach approach is now operational and that the ancient assessor commission has been formally dissolved.

